(2759, 220, 'additional_info', 'Andy Levi is vice president, publisher development, where he manages and sources relationships with major demand partners for Programmatic+. \r\n\r\nLevi has spent the entirety of his career working with the buy and sell side of the advertising industry. Levi launched his career in digital media at Adify, where he worked to build out their publisher development. While at the company, he did X (do we have an example of what he accomplished?). Levi joined Cox when the company acquired Adify in 2008. \r\n\r\nLevi holds a degree from Washington University in St. Louis.'),
