(2771, 216, 'additional_info', 'Katharine Zaki is vice president, finance and operational process management at Gamut. In this role, she oversees all finance and sales operations for the business.\r\n\r\nPreviously, Zaki worked at Bliss, where she ran financial planning and analytics for three lines of business, including: direct-to-consumer, e-commerce and wholesale. In this role, Zaki worked under the CFO, negotiating deals for international and domestic market expansions as well as product distribution deals for international markets, including Asia, the Middle East and Latin America. \r\n\r\nZaki also held roles at Columbia House and Miramax Films, where she prepared analysis for their international distribution division.\r\n\r\nA graduate of New York Universitys Stern School of Business, she holds a dual-degree in finance and international business.'),
