(2795, 224, 'additional_info', 'Lauren Halpern is vice president of CrossMedia+ at Gamut. In this capacity, Halpern manages the delivery of custom solutions for fully-integrated, multi-market, cross-screen campaigns, providing access to key audiences based on premier televised events.\r\n\r\nHalpern has a long history in sales leadership, with a focus on media and sports. Prior to joining Cox, Halperin served as the top sales post for Voltari in the mobile/digital space. She has held various positions within the media industry, including team leader for FOX Sports Media Group, account executive at Discovery Communications, and vice president of sales at The WB/CW Television Network, where she oversaw national and local sales.  Prior to her sales roles, Lauren worked on premium sports and entertainment accounts in national television buying at BBDO/OMD.  \r\n\r\nA graduate of University of Maryland College Park, Halperin holds a degree in X.'),
