(4637, 346, 'sidebar-intro', '<h2>What isprogrammatic?</h2>\r\nRefers to the usage of software with varying degrees of sophistication to purchase digital advertising, as opposed to the traditional process that involved RFPs, human negotiation and manual insertion orders.\r\n<h2>What is RTB?</h2>\r\nThe buying and selling of individual online ad impressions through real-time auctions that occur in the time it takes a webpage to load.\r\n\r\nDownload our insightfulProgrammatic+ Whitepaper to learn more.'),
